<DATE>03/03/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Glen</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>This is my second xterra. First was a 05 off-road 6speed. The new one is the same. 6 speed off-roads are soooo rare, had to jump at a new one. Still the best all around choice in a respectable 4x4 suv that can go "off-road" for real. But would like lower gears and a little more ground clearance. On the road, if you like power, this is the suv for the money.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>For under 30k you got something that really goes. Can chirp tires when you hit second. And it can go off road,even has a low range and a locker.</FAVORITE>
